// Widget Binding Names (match C++ meta=(BindWidget)):
// - CategorySwitcher
// - GameplayButton through MultiplayerButton
// - ApplyButton, SaveButton, ResetButton, CancelButton
// - All sliders, checkboxes, and combo boxes as named

// Styling Notes:
// - Category buttons: Highlight active category
// - Sliders: Show current values next to them
// - Checkboxes: Use custom styling for better visibility
// - High contrast mode: Alternative styling for all elements
// - All text should be scalable for accessibility

// Input Support:
// - Tab navigation through all controls
// - Arrow key navigation in combo boxes
// - Space/Enter to activate buttons/checkboxes
// - Escape to close settings

